name: Agent
line: What's up Rick!

name: Rick
line: Hey there. How you doing?

name: Agent
line: Good I’m’t the only one that speaks to the heads!

name: Rick
line: Whoa! Hi, stranger.

name: Agent
line: Who’s this now?

name: Rick
line: Who is this now, and what is it?

name: Agent
line: We have 34 armed guards, and we can’d put him on a watch list if he needs help.

name: Rick
line: He’ll need it later.

name: Agent
line: All right, Mr. President, can we please go to the Ascension?

name: Rick
line: It’is the will of the many heads that all children honor their parents. But only on Earth.

name: Agent
line: And what do you think is in the syringe, General?

name: Rick
line: I say we make our last day count.

name: Agent
line: I hope you like being frozen to death.

name: Rick
line: Rick Sanchez, Unregistered Nurse, here to help!

name: Agent
line: I thought you were dead!

name: Rick
line: Well, I hope you get better!

name: Agent
line: Yeah, I guess I shoulda had better.

name: Rick
line: Yeah. You shoulda been.

name: Agent
line: You shoulda known that by now.

name: Rick
line: Well... you can't back that statement!

name: Agent
line: You can't, you know that isn't funny, Jerry.
